        <h1 >
            Strong security for wireless remote control
        </h1>
    
    
     


    </div>
</div>

<div class="filterenabled spot-wrapper"  >
    
    <div class="article-wrapper">
        <div class="article-content clearfix textspot-content">
            
    io-homecontrol<sup>&reg;</sup> is a highly secure technology that VELUX INTEGRA<sup>&reg;</sup> and VELUX ACTIVE products use to communicate wirelessly with each other. The security level is comparable to the communication channels between an ATM and a bank.
    


        </div>
    </div>
